      "name": "Man-o-War (1st Rate)",
      "desc": "First rate. One hundred guns. Three gun decks. A thousand men. The floating castle that every navy builds precisely one of, because a second would bankrupt the treasury. She is the prestige weapon of an empire \u2014 more symbol than warship, but a symbol that can reduce a coastal city to rubble in an afternoon.",
